{"tid":58544,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解鑽牆一定要係九點？有冇裝修撚入黎解釋？","createTime":"2016-12-29T02:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T01:22:46.000Z","uid":1227,"like":44,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"adaa6c524bb0aa7df0b95b49fc2dd0b3b0cb04d2","tid":58544,"uid":1227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:06:15.000Z","msg":"純粹好奇，已經習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地係唔識係晏晝鑽定係行規要朝早鑽？<br />\n我發現佢地朝早會做哂最嘈既工序，晏晝11點幾到點幾就唔見人，有開工但好細聲，3點又唔見人。<br />\n定係覺得自己咁早開工，要攬住你班冚家剷一穫熟？<br />\n定係朝早好鑽啲，易入啲？"},{"pid":"4f24c8597b600dbfc15d2ac3146004512afa0a5d","tid":58544,"uid":8554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次訓訓下教一到九點幾十點就開始鑽<br />\n但晏晝又唔撚鑽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f3b1bc827f94d465cb56fc8884e8f9f6ae8789","tid":58544,"uid":27885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純粹好奇，已經習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地係唔識係晏晝鑽定係行規要朝早鑽？<br />\n我發現佢地朝早會做哂最嘈既工序，晏晝11點幾到點幾就唔見人，有開工但好細聲，3點又唔見人。<br />\n定係覺得自己咁早開工，要攬住你班冚家剷一穫熟？<br />\n定係朝早好鑽啲，易入啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朝早鑽 易入啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035e5d896af0123313fb7396035d19445b59a88b","tid":58544,"uid":6745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純粹好奇，已經習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地係唔識係晏晝鑽定係行規要朝早鑽？<br />\n我發現佢地朝早會做哂最嘈既工序，晏晝11點幾到點幾就唔見人，有開工但好細聲，3點又唔見人。<br />\n定係<span style=\"color: red;\">覺得自己咁早開工，要攬住你班冚家剷一穫熟</span>？<br />\n定係朝早好鑽啲，易入啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正確答案"},{"pid":"4851f29d46451ef1a12a384246e6e083e2df83d9","tid":58544,"uid":1227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次訓訓下教一到九點幾十點就開始鑽<br />\n但晏晝又唔撚鑽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪因為唔識分配工作先要做裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做唔到要用腦既行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b917a30364477e656fc225decfb18048bff30361","tid":58544,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:13:14.000Z","msg":"吉時"},{"pid":"6ea16c9fd30ff045c457ab955dded480e82ef65a","tid":58544,"uid":1227,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>純粹好奇，已經習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地係唔識係晏晝鑽定係行規要朝早鑽？<br />\n我發現佢地朝早會做哂最嘈既工序，晏晝11點幾到點幾就唔見人，有開工但好細聲，3點又唔見人。<br />\n定係<span style=\"color: red;\">覺得自己咁早開工，要攬住你班冚家剷一穫熟</span>？<br />\n定係朝早好鑽啲，易入啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正確答案</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲仆街冚家剷唔值得尊重<br />\n希望多啲工業意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744ccac21c55036630a59a83edd2862f473b4db1","tid":58544,"uid":14758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"頭先又比佢地鑽醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61ed20ef346fb829b75db04ad8802b65c12d1c9","tid":58544,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"早D搞掂早D收工"},{"pid":"e062039dbf219cd7868af2698407c3048965f29f","tid":58544,"uid":445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純粹好奇，已經習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地係唔識係晏晝鑽定係行規要朝早鑽？<br />\n我發現佢地朝早會做哂最嘈既工序，晏晝11點幾到點幾就唔見人，有開工但好細聲，3點又唔見人。<br />\n定係覺得自己咁早開工，要攬住你班冚家剷一穫熟？<br />\n定係朝早好鑽啲，易入啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔鑽窿先點做之後嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 文職"},{"pid":"c9fe25626666fbd5fbcf7e772d52785750c98b8e","tid":58544,"uid":6822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"因為鑽左牆先裝到野 正如你唔會未打樁就起到樓咁 如果你問點解唔係下晝鑽 第二朝裝野 咁係因為比錢果條友想快啲起到貨比佢<br />\n<br />\n係咪我真心左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36634746a393a7ba9681c0bc6de7b6955f80a578","tid":58544,"uid":18913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:27:17.000Z","msg":"唔鑽點做之後既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e3b9286e94d9d94f815ee024d5bdb9238208a1","tid":58544,"uid":21014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"三行佬開工時間<br />\n9-12（做野）<br />\n12-1 （食飯）<br />\n1-3 （做野）<br />\n3:45-5:45（做野）<br />\n5:45-6:00（準備收工）"},{"pid":"36c8286ae74c9397878dafe747e74a9f53709b4b","tid":58544,"uid":60023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三行佬開工時間<br />\n9-12（做野）<br />\n12-1 （食飯）<br />\n1-3 （做野）<br />\n3:45-5:45（做野）<br />\n5:45-6:00（準備收工）</blockquote><br />\n點解1-5:45 要分開"},{"pid":"bef13f184ddedd4e61d2bc2b9052f0b552218a88","tid":58544,"uid":33221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:29:51.000Z","msg":"已經鑽緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d04fa3ecc0370c2e10f71b468936d86e8d6057","tid":58544,"uid":66634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三行佬開工時間<br />\n9-12（做野）<br />\n12-1 （食飯）<br />\n1-3 （做野）<br />\n3:45-5:45（做野）<br />\n5:45-6:00（準備收工）</blockquote><br />\n點解1-5:45 要分開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為中間有45分鐘tea time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462e9345cfb22db1b99c446e6281658384bf732c","tid":58544,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:33:11.000Z","msg":"最早可以9點開工佢咪9點開<br />\n有阻滯都有充裕時間補救, 萬一做唔切, 夜晚又唔做得, 咪要delay成日<br />\n<br />\n可能佢啲task一般係鐅嘢先你咪覺得佢玩嘢"},{"pid":"7f4199d0e7d2f80454ede7472c0ffaf9f3f86465","tid":58544,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三行佬開工時間<br />\n9-12（做野）<br />\n12-1 （食飯）<br />\n1-3 （做野）<br />\n3:45-5:45（做野）<br />\n5:45-6:00（準備收工）</blockquote><br />\n點解1-5:45 要分開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解睇唔到少左45分"},{"pid":"488b50194961b90d616ef78231073a2cc81eb19e","tid":58544,"uid":1227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三行佬開工時間<br />\n9-12（做野）<br />\n12-1 （食飯）<br />\n1-3 （做野）<br />\n3:45-5:45（做野）<br />\n5:45-6:00（準備收工）</blockquote><br />\n點解1-5:45 要分開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為中間有45分鐘tea time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾撚嘆"},{"pid":"8cb0e953a1292120b5884554347254c28a22c5a0","tid":58544,"uid":1227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最早可以9點開工佢咪9點開<br />\n有阻滯都有充裕時間補救, 萬一做唔切, 夜晚又唔做得, 咪要delay成日<br />\n<br />\n可能佢啲task一般係鐅嘢先你咪覺得佢玩嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初初都會燥，宜家享受緊啲交響樂<br />\n我果邊有兩邊開緊工，一遠一近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191dc967922131d1069d83e2eb2d895d618bf8be","tid":58544,"uid":1227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最早可以9點開工佢咪9點開<br />\n有阻滯都有充裕時間補救, 萬一做唔切, 夜晚又唔做得, 咪要delay成日<br />\n<br />\n可能佢啲task一般係鐅嘢先你咪覺得佢玩嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晏晝做嘈既野，例如鑽牆<br />\n鑽完收工，第日朝早繼續唔得？<br />\n野都係咁做，但大家都舒服啲，定係又有原因？"},{"pid":"c5f98719596a467ca7f6889e8b73d02caa453749","tid":58544,"uid":1227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為鑽左牆先裝到野 正如你唔會未打樁就起到樓咁 如果你問點解唔係下晝鑽 第二朝裝野 咁係因為比錢果條友想快啲起到貨比佢<br />\n<br />\n係咪我真心左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晏晝鑽都可以快架，睇下點分工架姐"},{"pid":"65625a206d7e91ef1ea1e18a3a38283d36344c96","tid":58544,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"吉時"},{"pid":"4c34decde82763fdcfa3b927f22fe36050bf6415","tid":58544,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"人地好心叫醒你返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775eaa155eb5b9d2437fa4f19ec45391b6c0b05f","tid":58544,"uid":21262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:43:51.000Z","msg":"星期六朝早8點50分鑽打鑽到12點停 我個日好似冇訓過咁攰到仆街"},{"pid":"1d0b80116f95af0c83da196065c1cceef79fc3ad","tid":58544,"uid":39352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"應該排撚哂時間表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獲獲朝早先排到鑽牆"},{"pid":"e87a62d93c8aaf1deae7d66e384a60c9ac2a8d9a","tid":58544,"uid":15586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:46:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84e5d688be762c6321679c4555bac673dcb695e1","tid":58544,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:50:20.000Z","msg":"油漆泥水要時間乾"},{"pid":"a536bdcc39bf947e55c4979258935d0cb21d2f31","tid":58544,"uid":9804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:51:46.000Z","msg":"真係好撚嘈好撚困擾 屌佢老味<br />\n不過又唔係佢既錯，無藉口出去屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7986caff536f481fdf6892fd7310a0fdd032c77","tid":58544,"uid":69893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:52:54.000Z","msg":"因為鑽牆係成個工程係最煩嘅嘢，一鑽錯成千古恨。除咗鑽牆要用電鑽仲有拆牆、拆板、拆櫃都要用㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n要定哂位、鑽好哂先做到其他嘢，例如吸塵、上油、上電器之類，所以愈早鑽哂就愈多後續時間做其他嘢"},{"pid":"370ee5acde936aea1ddbbd7baeba9297f1bccf10","tid":58544,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最早可以9點開工佢咪9點開<br />\n有阻滯都有充裕時間補救, 萬一做唔切, 夜晚又唔做得, 咪要delay成日<br />\n<br />\n可能佢啲task一般係鐅嘢先你咪覺得佢玩嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晏晝做嘈既野，例如鑽牆<br />\n鑽完收工，第日朝早繼續唔得？<br />\n野都係咁做，但大家都舒服啲，定係又有原因？</blockquote><br />\n我又唔係裝修佬, 想我點答你? <br />\n我只係嘗試用時間管理角度諗原因<br />\n你想知咪自己去個單位敲門問人點解囉"},{"pid":"95f375b814f8067057baee69fbea5ed241c4fab2","tid":58544,"uid":3324,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:55:27.000Z","msg":"唔好再問落去，呢行有啲野唔信邪唔得"},{"pid":"a8b16070512c11809d6c8506356c49df98f10022","tid":58544,"uid":9814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:56:10.000Z","msg":"年尾日日鑽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8a32bf4b385bdcd8e936950d8a063a2a918c96","tid":58544,"uid":52270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:57:51.000Z","msg":"心諗：鑽完就輕輕鬆鬆食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嘈醒你關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"040e2bdc1022c7592b7d549ec8fe10fbc21c088e","tid":58544,"uid":29863